data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION Give some TLC to this NO HOA, island pool home situated on .42 acres. This home offers convenience and accessibility. LOCATED  just minutes from the beach, "A" rated schools, shopping, downtown and more.  With 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, this home offers a spacious living arrangement. The large climate-controlled Florida room is perfect for entertaining or watching the game. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances and a pass-through window, making it easy to serve guests. Cozy up in front of the wood-burning fireplace in the sunlit living room, or step outside to your inground 8-foot deep pool.   In the master bedroom, you'll find 8-foot sliding glass doors overlooking the back yard and pool area.    HVAC and roof replaced in 2017, providing peace of mind. Additionally, the property features an irrigation system, plenty of attic storage and is located on a court. This island pool home offers a spacious layout, great location and lots of privacy.
